        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>modern French ceramics styles [300106332], modern French decorative arts styles and movements [300021288], modern French styles and movements [300021265], modern European regional styles and movements [300021175], modern European styles and movements [300021424], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
